com.nutiteq.vectordatasources
Class AbstractVectorTileDataSource

java.lang.Object
  com.nutiteq.vectordatasources.AbstractVectorTileDataSource
All Implemented Interfaces:
VectorTileDataSource
public abstract class AbstractVectorTileDataSource
extends java.lang.Object
implements VectorTileDataSource

Abstract base class for vector tile datasources. It is recommended to use this as a base class for all vector tile datasources. This class provides default implementation for listener registration and other common datasource methods. Subclasses only need to define their loadTile method.
